y"></picture></a></div><div class=3D"c-article-section__figure-description"=
 data-test=3D"bottom-caption" id=3D"figure-1-desc"><p>Variance vs mean of <=
i>Q</i>. This scatter plot of Var[<i>Q</i>]/(<i>K</i>=E2=88=921) vs. E[<i>Q=
</i>]/(<i>K</i>=E2=88=921) contains the results of simulations of the momen=
ts of <i>Q</i>
