le/10.1186/s12874-015-0034-x#ref-CR16" id=3D"ref-link-section-d57159360e399=
5">16</a>], Lui and Chang [<a data-track=3D"click" data-track-action=3D"ref=
erence anchor" data-track-label=3D"link" data-test=3D"citation-ref" aria-la=
