ght function=20
</p><div id=3D"Equ8" class=3D"c-article-equation"><div class=3D"c-article-e=
quation__content"><span class=3D"mathjax-tex"> $$ \widehat{w}_{i}=3D f_{i}(=
\widehat{\theta}_{i}, \widehat{\zeta}_{i})=3D\left[\frac{(1+e^{\widehat{\th=
eta}_{i}+\widehat{\zeta}_{i}})^{2}}{(n_{Ti}+1)e^{\widehat{\theta}_{i}+\wide=
hat{\zeta}_{i}}} +\frac{(1+e^{\widehat{\zeta}_{i}})^{2}}{(n_{Ci}+1)e^{\wide=
hat{\zeta}_{i}}}\right]^{-1}   $$ </span></div><div class=3D"c-article-equa=
tion__number">
                    ((8))
                </div></div>
                        <p>The formulas below require that the central mome=
nts of <span class=3D"mathjax-tex">\(\widehat {\theta }_{i}\)</span> and <s=
pan class=3D"mathjax-tex">\(\widehat {\zeta }_{i}\)</span> satisfy the foll=
owing order conditions: <span class=3D"mathjax-tex">\(O(\text {E}[\Theta _{=
i}]) =3D1/{n_{i}^{2}}\)</span>, <span class=3D"mathjax-tex">\(O({\text {E}[=
\Theta _{i}^{2}}]) =3D1/n_{i}\)</span>, <span class=3D"mathjax-tex">\(O({\t=
ext {E}[\Theta _{i}^{3}}]) =3D1/{n_{i}^{2}}\)</span> and <span class=3D"mat=
hjax-tex">\(O({\text {E}[\Theta _{i}^{4}}]) =3D1/{n_{i}^{2}}\)</span> and s=
